Interface NearestNeighborsDigraphSupplier

All Known Implementing Classes:
DirectedToNNDigraph, UndirectedToNNDigraph
public interface NearestNeighborsDigraphSupplier
This interface is implemented by a class which reads edges of an undirected weighted linkageGraph, and by another class for the directed case.
Author:
R. W. R. Darling
